      PARAMETER (IDMN=49, JDMN=35, IF=20, IA=16, NOBPTS= 1,NBN=1)


C some notes

c idmn must be greater or equal to the number of columns (E-W) in grid
c jdmn must be greater or equal to the number of rows (N-S) in grid
c IF   must be greater or equal to the number of frequencies in spectrum
C IA   must be greater or equal to the number of angles in spectrum   
c keep last two parameters = 1
